https://medium.com/@satishios25/grpc-communication-between-micro-services-in-node-js-express-5a5c31ff8b6b
Task 
A simple blog application with two types of users:

    Users (content creators) - can create, read, update, delete, like, dislike blog posts
    Users should also be able to filter out blogs liked and disliked by them.
    Users need to be authenticated.
    User - should have at least username, password
    
    Viewers (content readers) - can only read blog posts
    
    Blog - should have at least title, content and author
    
    Analytics - Analytics endpoint to see total number of users and blogs
